{
  "id": "adv_bond_rui_01_04",
  "title": "天動瑠依4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと、DVDデッキのリモコンは……\nあった。再生っと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's see‚ where is the DVD player remote…\nFound it. Let's hit play.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.666666700001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、何か観るんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ are you watching something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "葵におすすめの映画DVDを借りたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I borrowed a DVD recommended by Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "アクションもので、主人公役のアイドルの子の演技が\nいいから観てほしいんだって。瑠依も一緒に観る？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's an action movie‚ and she said the lead idol girl's\nacting is great and worth watching. Want to join‚ Rui?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.2999991099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "演技の仕事の参考になるかもしれないですし\nご一緒させて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might be helpful for future acting roles.\nI'd love to join you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1333324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　ちょっと待って……？\nアクション映画って聞いたけどこれって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Wait a second…?\nI heard it was an action movie‚ but this is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ……ホラー映画ですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… it's a horror movie…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.0333325704,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_horror-voice-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.6674296
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "確かにアクション要素もあるけど……きゃぁああ\nなんで急に音が大きくなったの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ it does have action elements‚ but… Aaaah!\nWhy did the volume suddenly go up!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7999994915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……すみません\nリモコンの音量ボタン、間違って押しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… I'm sorry.\nI pressed the volume button on the remote by mistake.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.4666687013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと！　不用意に驚かさないで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously! Don't scare me like that without warning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.900001526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "演技と言ってもずっと叫ぶシーンばかりじゃない！\n瑠依はさっきから黙ってるけど……どう？　……瑠依？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it's acting‚ all she does is scream in every scene!\nRui‚ you've been quiet for a while… What do you think? …Rui?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4333368939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……すぅ、すぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Zzz‚ zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2666702272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "あ……寝てる\n疲れてたのに、無理に付き合わせちゃったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… she's asleep.\nI guess I forced her to stay up when she was tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2000035605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "きゃぁああ！　なんなの！？\nやだ！　えっ！？　誰かのいたずら！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaaaah! What's happening!?\nNo! Wait‚ what!? Is someone playing a prank!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4333358766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、瑠依！！　起きて！　私を一人にしないで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Rui!! Wake up! Don't leave me alone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1000025433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……むぅ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Mmm…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.0333338421,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1843.3333331999934
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2266.667683899996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "あ……沙季。他のみんなも……えぇ？\n一斉に電化製品を使ってブレーカーが落ちた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… Saki. And the others too… Wait‚ what?\nThe circuit breaker tripped because everyone used appliances at once?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.300001526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことだったの。ちょっと驚いたけど、大丈夫よ\nそれじゃ、みんなお休みなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that was it. I was a bit startled‚ but I'm fine.\nWell then‚ goodnight everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9333348593,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7666.667683900002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "一回止まっちゃったし、続きを観る気にならないわね\n私もそろそろ部屋に戻ろうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it stopped once‚ I'm not in the mood to keep watching.\nI should probably head back to my room too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7333374025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……すぅ……すぅ……んん……逃げてっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Zzz… zzz… mmm… Run away!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1333374025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "きゃあああ！　次は何！？　何が起きてるの！？\n……え、寝言……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaaaaaah! Now what!? What's going on!?\n…Oh‚ was that a sleep-talk…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.3666625978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ～。莉央さん、驚かさないで下さいよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yawn~ Rio-san‚ don't scare me like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.2333292645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_04-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "驚かしたのはあんたでしょ！\nほんっとにびっくりしたんだから！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're the one who scared me!\nYou really gave me a heart attack!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0333272299,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}